snippet.textDisplay: This whole song is a sad reality of Kashmir nowadays, no matter how flashy they portray their life to be. It’s sad and unfortunate what girls go through before, during and after marriage in Kashmir . These are indirect demands by the society and in laws, brushed under the blanket of fake smiles, artificial personalities and false promises. My heart cries for the girls of my beautiful valley and their parents. Such People in Kashmir have the ugliest faces beneath their wealth, superiority and show off and they set bad examples for everyone. May Allah be with us and all the women and their families , and bring kindness in our hearts! 💔
